---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Vizino AI - Transform Your Interior Design Vision into Reality" 
  description="AI-powered interior design visualization. Upload your room, preview paint colors, textures, and furnishings with precision. No design background needed."
>
  <!-- Introduction Section -->
  <section class="intro-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="intro-content">
        <h1>Transform Your Interior Design Vision into Reality</h1>
        <p>Upload your room photo and instantly preview how different paint colors, textures, and furnishings look. No design background needed—AI does the heavy lifting.</p>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
          <a href="#cta" class="btn btn-primary">Join Beta Program</a>
          <a href="#how-it-works" class="btn btn-secondary">See How It Works</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="intro-visual">
        <div class="preview-mockup">
          <div class="mockup-header">Room Preview</div>
          <div class="mockup-content">
            <div class="color-preview"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Features Section -->
  <section id="features" class="features-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Why Choose Vizino AI</h2>
        <p>Designed for interior designers, architects, and homeowners who value precision and efficiency</p>
      </div>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <!-- Feature 1: Custom Material Library -->
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none">
              <rect width="40" height="40" rx="8" fill="#e0e7ff"/>
              <g stroke="#4f46e5" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round">
                <path d="M13 14h14M13 20h14M13 26h10"/>
                <rect x="13" y="12" width="14" height="16" rx="2"/>
              </g>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Custom Material Library</h3>
          <p>Organize your design projects and spaces like never before. Keep all your materials, references, and inspirations in one place—no more getting lost in chat history.</p>
          <ul class="feature-list">
            <li>Create and manage multiple projects</li>
            <li>Organize spaces within each project</li>
            <li>Store custom colors, textures & assets</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Feature 2: Custom Prompts & AI -->
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none">
              <rect width="40" height="40" rx="8" fill="#e0e7ff"/>
              <g stroke="#4f46e5" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round">
                <path d="M11 18c0-3.314 2.686-6 6-6s6 2.686 6 6-2.686 6-6 6h-2l-4 3v-3h-2c-3.314 0-6-2.686-6-6z"/>
                <path d="M20 15h4M20 18h6M20 21h4"/>
              </g>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>AI-Powered Prompts</h3>
          <p>Craft custom prompts with AI-assisted writing. Leverage the cutting-edge Nano Banana model for the most accurate and stunning visualizations.</p>
          <ul class="feature-list">
            <li>Smart prompt suggestions</li>
            <li>Advanced AI image generation</li>
            <li>Iterative refinement tools</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Feature 3: Design Precision -->
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none">
              <rect width="40" height="40" rx="8" fill="#e0e7ff"/>
              <g stroke="#4f46e5" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <circle cx="20" cy="20" r="8"/>
                <path d="M20 11v-2M20 31v2M29 20h2M9 20h2M27.07 12.93l1.41-1.41M11.52 28.48l1.41-1.41M27.07 27.07l1.41 1.41M11.52 11.52l1.41 1.41"/>
              </g>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>No Design Background Required</h3>
          <p>Turn imagination into pixel-perfect reality. Instantly generate professional preview images with precision—making it easier to communicate with contractors, designers, and clients.</p>
          <ul class="feature-list">
            <li>Instant preview generation</li>
            <li>Professional-quality output</li>
            <li>Easy collaboration & communication</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Feature 4: Time & Cost Savings -->
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none">
              <rect width="40" height="40" rx="8" fill="#e0e7ff"/>
              <g stroke="#4f46e5" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M20 13v14M16 17h8M16 23h8"/>
                <circle cx="20" cy="20" r="9"/>
              </g>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Save Time & Money</h3>
          <p>Make confident design decisions before buying materials. Eliminate costly mistakes, reduce multiple paint tests, and accelerate your project timeline.</p>
          <ul class="feature-list">
            <li>Reduce design iterations</li>
            <li>Minimize material waste</li>
            <li>Speed up decision-making</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Who Uses Vizino Studio Section -->
  <section class="who-uses-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Who Uses Vizino Studio?</h2>
        <p>Trusted by design professionals and homeowners alike</p>
      </div>
      <div class="who-uses-grid">
        <div class="who-card">
          <div class="who-icon">
            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none">
              <rect width="40" height="40" rx="8" fill="#e0e7ff"/>
              <g stroke="#4f46e5" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M12 28h16M12 24h16M12 20h16M15 12h10v8H15z"/>
              </g>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Interior Designers</h3>
          <p>Showcase concepts and variations to clients instantly with professional visualizations.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="who-card">
          <div class="who-icon">
            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none">
              <rect width="40" height="40" rx="8" fill="#e0e7ff"/>
              <g stroke="#4f46e5" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M20 10l-8 8v12h16V18l-8-8z"/>
                <path d="M17 28v-8h6v8"/>
              </g>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Architects</h3>
          <p>Explore design alternatives and material combinations quickly during project planning.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="who-card">
          <div class="who-icon">
            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none">
              <rect width="40" height="40" rx="8" fill="#e0e7ff"/>
              <g stroke="#4f46e5" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <circle cx="20" cy="15" r="4"/>
                <path d="M12 28c0-4.418 3.582-8 8-8s8 3.582 8 8"/>
              </g>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Homeowners & DIY Enthusiasts</h3>
          <p>Get inspiration and visualize home improvement projects before making decisions.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="who-card">
          <div class="who-icon">
            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none">
              <rect width="40" height="40" rx="8" fill="#e0e7ff"/>
              <g stroke="#4f46e5" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <rect x="12" y="13" width="16" height="14" rx="2"/>
                <path d="M12 18h16M20 13v5"/>
              </g>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Real Estate Professionals</h3>
          <p>Enhance property listings with stunning AI-generated interior visualizations.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How It Works Section -->
  <section id="how-it-works" class="how-it-works-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>How It Works</h2>
        <p>Simple, intuitive workflow for beautiful results</p>
      </div>
      <div class="steps-grid">
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">01</div>
          <h3>Upload & Organize</h3>
          <p>Take a photo of your room or upload from your device. Create a new project and space to keep everything organized.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step-arrow">→</div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">02</div>
          <h3>Customize & Generate</h3>
          <p>Choose paint colors, textures, furniture, or write a custom prompt. AI instantly generates a preview of your design concept.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step-arrow">→</div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">03</div>
          <h3>Compare & Refine</h3>
          <p>View before/after comparisons. Iterate and experiment until you achieve the perfect design—then save or share with others.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Real Examples Section -->
  <section class="examples-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Real Design Transformations</h2>
        <p>See how Vizino AI helps bring design visions to life</p>
      </div>
      <div class="examples-grid">
        <div class="example-card">
          <div class="example-before-after">
            <div class="example-image original" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef3c7 0%, #fde68a 100%);">
              <span class="label">Before</span>
            </div>
            <div class="example-image transformed" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dbeafe 0%, #bfdbfe 100%);">
              <span class="label">After</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <h4>Modern Minimalist</h4>
          <p>Cream walls transformed to soft blue with contemporary furniture styling</p>
        </div>

        <div class="example-card">
          <div class="example-before-after">
            <div class="example-image original" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f3e8ff 0%, #fae8ff 100%);">
              <span class="label">Before</span>
            </div>
            <div class="example-image transformed" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dbeafe 0%, #bae6fd 100%);">
              <span class="label">After</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <h4>Scandinavian Elegance</h4>
          <p>Neutral palette enhanced with cool tones and minimalist décor</p>
        </div>

        <div class="example-card">
          <div class="example-before-after">
            <div class="example-image original" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f3ff 0%, #ede9fe 100%);">
              <span class="label">Before</span>
            </div>
            <div class="example-image transformed" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d1fae5 0%, #a7f3d0 100%);">
              <span class="label">After</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <h4>Warm & Inviting</h4>
          <p>Soft green tones create a calming, nature-inspired atmosphere</p>
        </div>

        <div class="example-card">
          <div class="example-before-after">
            <div class="example-image original" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef2f2 0%, #fee2e2 100%);">
              <span class="label">Before</span>
            </div>
            <div class="example-image transformed" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e293b 0%, #334155 100%);">
              <span class="label">After</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <h4>Modern Drama</h4>
          <p>Bold dark tones for a sophisticated, contemporary look</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Beta Program Section -->
  <section id="beta" class="beta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="beta-content">
        <h2>Join Our Beta Program</h2>
        <p>Be among the first to experience the future of interior design visualization</p>
        
        <div class="beta-benefits">
          <div class="benefit">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
              <path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41L9 16.17Z" fill="#ffffff"/>
            </svg>
            <span><strong>Invitation-Only Access</strong> — Curated community of design professionals</span>
          </div>
          <div class="benefit">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
              <path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41L9 16.17Z" fill="#ffffff"/>
            </svg>
            <span><strong>V Points Credits</strong> — Complimentary credits for all beta participants</span>
          </div>
          <div class="benefit">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
              <path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41L9 16.17Z" fill="#ffffff"/>
            </svg>
            <span><strong>Direct Feedback Channel</strong> — Your input shapes the product</span>
          </div>
          <div class="benefit">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
              <path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41L9 16.17Z" fill="#ffffff"/>
            </svg>
            <span><strong>Priority Support</strong> — Dedicated assistance during beta phase</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section id="cta" class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <h2>Ready to Transform Your Design Process?</h2>
        <p>Join the beta program and start creating stunning interior design previews today</p>
        <a href="https://app.vizino.ai/auth" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">Get Access Now</a>
        <p class="cta-note">Sign up with your email to receive your invitation and V Points credits</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Introduction Section */
  .intro-section {
    padding: var(--spacing-4xl) 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand-violet-light) 0%, var(--color-gray-50) 100%);
  }

  .intro-section .container {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--spacing-4xl);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .intro-content h1 {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
    line-height: var(--line-height-tight);
  }

  .intro-content > p {
    font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
    color: var(--color-gray-600);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2xl);
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--spacing-lg);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  /* Preview Mockup */
  .preview-mockup {
    background-color: var(--color-white);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-xl);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .mockup-header {
    background-color: var(--color-gray-100);
    padding: var(--spacing-md);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);
    color: var(--color-gray-700);
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
  }

  .mockup-content {
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    background-color: var(--color-gray-50);
  }

  .color-preview {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f3e8ff 0%, #faf5ff 100%);
  }

  /* Section Header */
  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-4xl);
  }

  .section-header h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .section-header p {
    font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
    color: var(--color-gray-600);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* Features Section */
  .features-section {
    padding: var(--spacing-4xl) 0;
    background-color: var(--color-white);
  }

  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--spacing-2xl);
  }

  .feature-card {
    padding: var(--spacing-2xl);
    background-color: var(--color-gray-50);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-gray-200);
    transition: all var(--transition-base);
  }

  .feature-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--brand-indigo);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .feature-icon {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
    display: flex;
  }

  .feature-card h3 {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .feature-card > p {
    color: var(--color-gray-600);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
    line-height: var(--line-height-relaxed);
  }

  .feature-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding-left: 0;
  }

  .feature-list li {
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    color: var(--color-gray-600);
    padding-left: var(--spacing-md);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
    position: relative;
  }

  .feature-list li:before {
    content: '✓';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--brand-indigo);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-bold);
  }

  /* Who Uses Section */
  .who-uses-section {
    padding: var(--spacing-4xl) 0;
    background-color: var(--color-gray-50);
  }

  .who-uses-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--spacing-2xl);
  }

  .who-card {
    padding: var(--spacing-2xl);
    background-color: var(--color-white);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-gray-200);
    transition: all var(--transition-base);
  }

  .who-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--brand-indigo);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .who-icon {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
    display: flex;
  }

  .who-card h3 {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .who-card p {
    color: var(--color-gray-600);
    line-height: var(--line-height-relaxed);
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
  }

  /* How It Works Section */
  .how-it-works-section {
    padding: var(--spacing-4xl) 0;
    background-color: var(--color-white);
  }

  .steps-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--spacing-2xl);
    align-items: start;
    position: relative;
  }

  .step {
    padding: var(--spacing-2xl);
    background-color: var(--color-gray-50);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    border: 2px solid var(--color-gray-200);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .step-number {
    font-size: var(--font-size-4xl);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-bold);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand-indigo) 0%, var(--brand-violet) 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .step h3 {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .step p {
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    color: var(--color-gray-600);
    line-height: var(--line-height-relaxed);
  }

  .step-arrow {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: var(--font-size-2xl);
    color: var(--brand-indigo);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-bold);
  }

  /* Examples Section */
  .examples-section {
    padding: var(--spacing-4xl) 0;
    background-color: var(--color-gray-50);
  }

  .examples-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--spacing-2xl);
  }

  .example-card {
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    transition: all var(--transition-base);
    background-color: var(--color-white);
  }

  .example-card:hover {
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .example-before-after {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 2px;
    height: 250px;
  }

  .example-image {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    justify-content: center;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .example-image .label {
    background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
    color: var(--color-white);
    padding: var(--spacing-sm) var(--spacing-md);
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .example-card h4 {
    padding: var(--spacing-lg);
    padding-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .example-card p {
    padding: var(--spacing-lg);
    padding-top: var(--spacing-sm);
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    color: var(--color-gray-600);
  }

  /* Beta Section */
  .beta-section {
    padding: var(--spacing-4xl) 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand-indigo) 0%, var(--brand-violet) 100%);
    color: var(--color-white);
  }

  .beta-content h2,
  .beta-content > p {
    color: var(--color-white);
  }

  .beta-content {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .beta-content h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .beta-content > p {
    font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2xl);
  }

  .beta-benefits {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--spacing-2xl);
    margin-top: var(--spacing-2xl);
  }

  .benefit {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: var(--spacing-lg);
    text-align: left;
    padding: var(--spacing-lg);
    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
  }

  .benefit svg {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .benefit span {
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    line-height: var(--line-height-relaxed);
    color: var(--color-white);
  }

  /* CTA Section */
  .cta-section {
    padding: var(--spacing-4xl) 0;
    background-color: var(--color-white);
  }

  .cta-content {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .cta-content h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .cta-content > p:first-of-type {
    font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
    color: var(--color-gray-600);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2xl);
  }

  .cta-note {
    margin-top: var(--spacing-lg);
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    color: var(--color-gray-600);
  }

  /* Responsive Design */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .intro-section .container {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .intro-content h1 {
      font-size: var(--font-size-3xl);
    }

    .steps-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .step-arrow {
      display: none;
    }

    .cta-buttons {
